## Architecture Briefs

### Frontend (`public/scripts/`)

- **Types:** `types.ts` — Frontend type definitions. Self-contained; must NOT import from `src/`. Shared types are duplicated from `src/functions/types.ts` and kept in sync manually. Import from `./types.js` or `../types.js`.
- **Entry points:** `entry/` — student-mode, instructor-mode, course-selection
- **Features:** `feature/` — chat, documents, flags, monitor, assistant-prompts, system-prompts, course-information, student-flag-history, artefact, render-chat
- **Services:** `services/` — auth-service, rag-service, document-upload-module, inactivity-tracker (kebab-case filenames)
- **API helpers:** `api/` — api, chat-api
- **UI components:** `ui/` — modal-overlay, toast-notification, version-display
- **Auth:** `auth/` — auth-manager
- **Factories:** `factories/` — instructor-user-factory, student-user-factory
- **Onboarding:** `onboarding/` — course-setup, document-setup, flag-setup, monitor-setup, student-onboarding
- **Utilities:** `utils/` — url-parser

**Related docs:** See `documentation/` for implementation details. For chat changes, check `documentation/ENDPOINT_ARCHITECTURE.md` and `src/functions/ChatApp.ts`.

### Backend (`src/`)

- **Routes:** `auth`, `course-routes`, `chat-app`, `rag-routes`, `mongo-routes`, `course-entry`, `user-management`, `health`, `version`
- **Core:** `EngEAI_MongoDB` (singleton), `ChatApp`, `RAGApp`, `rag-app.ts`
- **Middleware:** `requireAuth`, `requireCourseRole`, `passport`, `session`

**Related docs:** `documentation/ENDPOINT_ARCHITECTURE.md` — routes, RBAC, API layout.

### Database (MongoDB)

- **Collections:** `active-course-list`, `active-users`, per-course collections (users, flags, memory-agent)
- **Core:** `EngEAI_MongoDB` in `src/functions/EngEAI_MongoDB.ts`
- **Data:** Courses, users, chats, flags, learning objectives, materials, system prompts

### Vector Database (Qdrant)

- **Access:** Via `RAGApp` and `ubc-genai-toolkit-rag` (RAGModule)
- **Use:** Document chunks, embeddings, similarity search for RAG
- **Storage:** Materials have `qdrantId`; course deletion cascades to Qdrant

