## Deployment

**EngE-AI is deployed on-premise** (hosted on UBC infrastructure, not cloud). Staging and prod run on the same infrastructure model.

### Staging

Staging is used to test before prod. It has no direct connection to prod. When the user asks for a list of tests to run in staging, provide a checklist of tests that validate the implementation.

### Prod

(No deployment workflow defined in rules.)

