## Summary

- Check versions and docs before coding; if docs missing/outdated, create or update them
- Agree before changing code; check in on every task
- Plan → Implement → Document → Test (see Workflow Example)
- Never edit `public/dist/*.js`
- Bump version on code changes
- Ask before providing tests (see Testing examples)
- Styling: suggest inside `<styling_AI_suggest>` only
- Files: lowercase, hyphen for multi-word (e.g. `try-hard.ts`)
- Variables: camelCase; classes/interfaces: PascalCase
- Interfaces in `types.ts`; shared types must match frontend and backend
- Remove or comment out `console.log` before finalizing
